{
  "text": "\u2022 For the cut metric d , is it the case that the function \u03c6 H , as defined in [CITATION_1] , can be expressed only in terms of p and of ed H (\u00b7)? \u2022 For any metric d that is continuous with respect to the edit metric, is it the case that the function \u03c6 H , as defined in (13), can be expressed only in terms of p and of ed H (\u00b7)?",
